snippet.title: Mecha BREAK - 6V6 Mecha Mayhem Trailer | Gamescom ONL 2024
snippet.description:
In the crucible of 6v6 combat, pilot the Mech that calls to you.

Are you a sniper, attacker, or defender? Join forces and forge victory with your main Striker!

For more information about Mecha BREAK and upcoming test schedules, please visit:
Mecha BREAK Official Website: https://www.mechabreak.com/en/#/
